author: akarasulu
msg: Moved ssl filter to new project.  I used org.apache.mina.ssl for the project
name rather than org.apache.mina.filter.support in the hope that we can have
a shorter name and that the package can be changed later.  Even though the
SSL code is a filter implementation in the support package it will be a
separate project to isolate it's needs as a 1.5 jdk build.
